### 1.3 Update `gvs_saved_growth_scenarios` (Saved Scenarios Table)

This table stores scenarios the founder explicitly saves. One row per saved scenario. Loaded without rerunning GPT.

#### Add New Columns

```sql
-- Link back to the originating runtime record
ALTER TABLE public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  ADD COLUMN runtime_scenario_id uuid NULL
    REFERENCES public.gvs_growth_scenarios (id) ON DELETE SET NULL;

-- GPT-generated synthesis content copied from runtime record at save time
ALTER TABLE public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  ADD COLUMN synthesis_content jsonb NULL;

-- Top-level score for display and sorting without parsing results JSONB
ALTER TABLE public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  ADD COLUMN gvi_score integer NULL;

-- Allows founder to pin a scenario as primary reference
ALTER TABLE public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  ADD COLUMN is_pinned boolean NOT NULL DEFAULT false;

-- Tracks re-saves of a named scenario over time
ALTER TABLE public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  ADD COLUMN version integer NOT NULL DEFAULT 1;
```

#### Add New Index

```sql
CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_gvs_saved_runtime_id
  ON public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios USING btree (runtime_scenario_id);

CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_gvs_saved_pinned
  ON public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios USING btree (user_id, is_pinned);
```

#### Full Table Definition (Post-Migration)

```sql
create table public.gvs_saved_growth_scenarios (
  id                    uuid not null default gen_random_uuid(),
  user_id               uuid not null,
  agency_id             uuid not null,
  runtime_scenario_id   uuid null,
  scenario_name         text not null,
  inputs                jsonb not null,
  results               jsonb not null,
  implications          jsonb null,
  synthesis_content     jsonb null,
  gvi_score             integer null,
  is_pinned             boolean not null default false,
  version               integer not null default 1,
  created_at            timestamp with time zone null default now(),
  updated_at            timestamp with time zone null default now(),
  constraint gvs_saved_growth_scenarios_pkey primary key (id),
  constraint gvs_saved_scenarios_agency_id_fkey
    foreign key (agency_id) references agencies (agency_id) on delete cascade,
  constraint gvs_saved_scenarios_user_id_fkey
    foreign key (user_id) references auth.users (id) on delete cascade,
  constraint gvs_saved_scenarios_runtime_id_fkey
    foreign key (runtime_scenario_id)
    references public.gvs_growth_scenarios (id) on delete set null
);
```

