### 1.4 Update Triggers

Rename existing triggers to match new table names and update function references.

```sql
-- Drop old triggers from original table names (already renamed)
-- Recreate on new table names

CREATE TRIGGER enforce_gvs_save_limit
  BEFORE INSERT ON gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION check_gvc_save_limit();

CREATE TRIGGER maintain_gvs_saves_count
  AFTER INSERT OR DELETE ON gvs_saved_growth_scenarios
  FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION update_gvc_saves_count();
```

> **Note:** The underlying functions `check_gvc_save_limit()` and `update_gvc_saves_count()` do not need to change unless their internal table references are hardcoded to the old names. Verify and update those function bodies if needed.

